Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.31,0:03:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Greetings from Ken Wap.\N>> Oh, hi. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.84,0:03:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Nice to meet you.\N>> Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.68,0:03:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Llan Church.\N>> Oh, boy. How are you?
